---
import SectionHeading from "../Elements/SectionHeading.astro";
import Button from "../Elements/Button.astro";
---

<section id="our-solution">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="text-content">
			<SectionHeading
				smallText="Our Solution"
				bigText="4Ever Homes and Communities"
			/>
			<p class="regular-text">
				Our hybrid sustainable homes with an integrated agriculture room save
				families $6000 + yearly. Our 4Ever Homes are developed faster than
				traditional homes, while still being cost effective. We have at this
				moment 57 acres of land for developing our vision, we have built
				relationships with manufactures and other key players along with
				volunteers and a social following of 80,000 + globally and growing.
			</p>
			<p class="regular-text">
				4Ever Homes is our brand of hybrid and sustainable homes that are
				designed to help families creating a new lifestyle by saving them
				money, increasing their food security, and allowing the creation of
				strong social bonds.
			</p>
			<div class="button">
				<Button
					href="#the-benefits"
					text="The Benefits"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="img">
			<img src="images/model-home-2.webp" />
		</div>
		<div class="img">
			<img src="images/model-home-4b.webp" />
		</div>
		<div class="img">
			<img src="images/model-home-1.webp" />
		</div>
		<div class="img">
			<img src="images/model-home-3.webp" />
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 43%;
		grid-template-rows: /* 3fr 2fr */ auto auto;
		gap: var(--fs-9) var(--fs-8);
	}

	.text-content {
		grid-column: span 2;
	}

	p:first-of-type {
		margin-top: var(--fs-8);
	}

	p + p {
		margin-top: var(--fs-5);
	}

	p:last-of-type {
		margin-bottom: var(--fs-7);
	}

	.button {
		margin-bottom: 80px;
	}

	.img {
		position: relative;
	}

	.img::after {
		content: "";

		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;

		background-color: #000000;

		opacity: 35%;
	}

	img {
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}
</style>
